# Sub-A test: F con 3 params + Call con 3 args.
# add3 [a, b, c]: tmp = a + b + c, retorna.
# Call add3 con 10, 20, 12. Exit con tmp = 42.
D 0 0 zero Integer 0
D 0 0 tmp Integer 0
D 0 0 partial Integer 0

F 0 0 add3 [a, b, c]
R 0 0 Add [a, b] partial
R 0 0 Add [partial, c] tmp
R 0 0 Ret []
R 0 0 EndF

R 0 0 Call [add3, 10, 20, 12]
R 0 0 ExitTop [tmp]
